OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then cloud and rain will
OL,7,Fspread southeast across all parts
OL,8,Fovernight followed by clearer weather
OL,9,Fand a few showers in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,12,Fshowers, these turning more widespread
OL,13,Fand occasionally heavy during the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Colder than of late.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry for
OL,17,Fmost of Friday before rain spreads
OL,18,Fnortheast by evening. Mainly dry and
OL,19,Fbright Saturday. Breezy with showers
OL,20,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
